=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_LeakDC_ex1 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 800 Hz, featuring instant attack and sustained envelope, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally rich.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: instant
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: rich
  spectral_flux_normalized: stable
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 800.0000
  harmonic_decay_rate: -2.8718
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0383
  pitch_clarity: 323.0901
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -1.6725
  resonance_freq: 753.6621

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: LeakDC Example 1
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/LeakDC.html
// Tags: LeakDC, Classes
// ---
// --- Example 1 ---
(
{
    var a;
    a = LFPulse.ar(800, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    [a, LeakDC.ar(a, 0.995)]
}.play
)
